@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gsrklu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(tmp)
    tmp = wp.cos((wp.sin(v1 + 0.07) / (v1 + 0.40 - v0 + 0.35)))
    tmp = v2
    v0 = (v1 - 0.56)
    v0 = (v1 - wp.exp(0.50))
    v2 = (v2 - (v2 + (tmp + 0.53 - v1 + 0.13)))
    data[tid] = v0
